{"tid":1712452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地唔撚理我再開 我屋企好多曱甴 幫拖","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T17:03:00.000Z","uid":215901,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2e3aec46274484b23af8319ed2c8d8df438fae","tid":1712452,"uid":215901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:25:09.000Z","msg":"屌佢地 夜一夜就成群出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n癲到開始唔驚人<br />\n我老豆老母又淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一唔驚個啲始終唔敢拍，因為佢地一飛好似子彈咁撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我決左無可能面對面殺佢地<br />\n偷偷趁佢地揾野食個陣落毒<br />\n已經發現佢地會係廚房去水位同另外幾點搵餅乾碎<br />\n日日放啲 唔覺唔覺<br />\n放完走埋佢都唔撚知係我老豆定老母放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終有一日佢帶番竇<br />\n就輕輕鬆鬆起哂佢全家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65252411f4ec3621c97ae6021b2a00f60546baa","tid":1712452,"uid":96648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a471288dbe2ebc0b6fec8e3ba3008d732ee61c","tid":1712452,"uid":215901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"兵法之首 先斷補給"},{"pid":"73c1b90b6f569bf4c1e10052a839e90a77221b92","tid":1712452,"uid":215901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e19450e349977eea88d5e0b55b3cac45897cc832","tid":1712452,"uid":215901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"603562e67d96cfcff5b6706d42696c7930c4495a","tid":1